Package: flac
Version: 1.0.2
Revision: 1
Source: mirror:sourceforge:%n/%n-%v-src.tar.gz
SourceDirectory: %n-%v
Patch: %f.patch
SetCFLAGS: -I%p/include
ConfigureParams: --mandir=%p/share/man
Depends: libogg-shlibs, xmms
InstallScript: << 
make install DESTDIR=%d 
<<
SplitOff: <<
  Package: %N-shlibs
  Files: lib/libFLAC.*.dylib 
  DocFiles: README COPYING.LGPL
<<
DocFiles: README AUTHORS COPYING.FDL COPYING.GPL COPYING.LGPL
Description: Free lossless audio codec.
DescDetail: <<
Includes XMMS plugin.
<<
DescPackaging: <<
Does not use pbxbuild method since we want dylibs, and
the xmms plugin. Also the make/config method puts everything in
the right place.
<<
License: GPL
Maintainer: Ben Hines <bhines@alumni.ucsd.edu>
Homepage: http://flac.sf.net/


